  (function () {
    var noop = function noop() {};
    if ("performance" in window === false) {
      window.performance = {};
    }
    window.performance.mark = performance.mark || noop;
    window.performance.measure = performance.measure || noop;
    if ("now" in window.performance === false) {
      var nowOffset = Date.now();
      if (performance.timing && performance.timing.navigationStart) {
        nowOffset = performance.timing.navigationStart;
      }
      window.performance.now = function now() {
        return Date.now() - nowOffset;
      };
    }
  })();

<script id="wix-first-paint">
    if (window.ResizeObserver &&
        (!window.PerformanceObserver || !PerformanceObserver.supportedEntryTypes || PerformanceObserver.supportedEntryTypes.indexOf('paint') === -1)) {
        new ResizeObserver(function (entries, observer) {
            entries.some(function (entry) {
                var contentRect = entry.contentRect;
                if (contentRect.width > 0 && contentRect.height > 0) {
                    requestAnimationFrame(function (now) {
                        window.wixFirstPaint = now;
                        dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('wixFirstPaint'));
                    });
                    observer.disconnect();
                    return true;
                }
            });
        }).observe(document.body);
    }
</script>

children’s self-confidence, speech and presentation skills through acting, and making props and learning the&nbsp; process of making a film.</span></p>

<p class="font_9 wixui-rich-text__text" style="text-align:justify; font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="font_9 wixui-rich-text__text" style="text-align:justify; font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Our drama component of the camp is throup adopting Michael Rosen’s “We’re Going on Bear Hunt”.&nbsp; Children will be listening to the story, creating the props, singing, dancing, acting, memorizing lines and actions and a lot more much more fun activities during the camp.</span></p>

<p class="font_9 wixui-rich-text__text" style="text-align:justify; font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="font_9 wixui-rich-text__text" style="text-align:justify; font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">The children will bring this fantastic story to life as the finale of the camp and we will forward you the video of their acting for your family and friends to enjoy.</span></p></div><div id="comp-kplyszji1" class="comp-kplyszji1" data-semantic-classname="button"><a data-testid="linkElement" data-anchor="dataItem-kpm030us" data-anchor-comp-id="comp-kpm030t6" href="https://www.rtmschool.com/copy-of-admissions" target="_self" class="StylableButton2545352419__root style-kplzb44a__root wixui-button StylableButton2545352419__link" aria-label="Week 2"><div class="StylableButton2545352419__container"><span class="StylableButton2545352419__label wixui-button__label" data-testid="stylablebutton-label">Week 2</span><span class="StylableButton2545352419__icon wixui-button__icon" aria-hidden="true" data-testid="stylablebutton-icon"><div><svg data-bbox="13.05 2.55 33.878 54.8" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 60 60">

id="comp-kokvcwk9" class="MazNVa comp-kokvcwk9 wixui-image"><div data-testid="linkElement" class="j7pOnl"><wow-image id="img_comp-kokvcwk9" class="HlRz5e BI8PVQ" class="SxM0TO QxJLC3 comp-kplzmwjd3 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_9 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">This ‘Summer Fun’ 5-day camp is catered for 2 – 6 years old. &nbsp;The aims are to improve children’s Gross and Fun motor skills, higher thinking skills and social emotional learning and development through a series of outdoor and indoor fun activities.</span></p>

<p class="font_9 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="font_9 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">We have a secluded and safe outdoor compound for the children to play various sports and games under the sun. &nbsp;Our classrooms are also cosily set up for children to carry out indoor games and activities during the camp.</span></p>

<p class="font_9 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="font_9 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">At the end of the week, the children will bring home with a photo album of all the activities that they have done during the camp.</span></p></div><div id="comp-kplzmwjg" class="comp-kplzmwjg" data-semantic-classname="button"><a data-testid="linkElement" data-anchor="dataItem-kpm02kbm" data-anchor-comp-id="comp-kpm02ka5" href="https://www.rtmschool.com/copy-of-admissions" target="_self" class="StylableButton2545352419__root style-kplzmwji1__root wixui-button StylableButton2545352419__link" aria-label="Week 1"><div class="StylableButton2545352419__container"><span class="StylableButton2545352419__label wixui-button__label" data-testid="stylablebutton-label">Week 1</span><span class="StylableButton2545352419__icon wixui-button__icon" aria-hidden="true" data-testid="stylablebutton-icon"><div><svg data-bbox="13.05 2.55 33.878 54.8" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 60 60">

class="SxM0TO QxJLC3 comp-kplztst04 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_9 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">The ‘I Am Creative’ 5-day camp is catered for 2 – 6 years old.&nbsp; The aims are to develop and improve children’s sensorial, fine motor skills, hands-on ability, creativity and imaginations.</span></p>

<p class="font_9 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class="font_9 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">During the week camp, there are lots of fun activities revolving the theme of the camp.&nbsp; They will be doing a cookery class where they learn the process of baking.&nbsp; Using colourful light non-toxic to Sculture objects is also an activity that children love.&nbsp; There will be painting and art classes that round up the theme too.</span></p>

<p class="font_9 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class="font_9 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:16px;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">The children will bring home with snapshots of them at play, art and craft creations and the gourmet that they have prepared during the camp.</span></p></div><div id="comp-kplztst2" class="comp-kplztst2" data-semantic-classname="button"><a data-testid="linkElement" data-anchor="dataItem-kpm030us" data-anchor-comp-id="comp-kpm030t6" href="https://www.rtmschool.com/copy-of-admissions" target="_self" class="StylableButton2545352419__root style-kplztst41__root wixui-button StylableButton2545352419__link" aria-label="Week 2"><div class="StylableButton2545352419__container"><span class="StylableButton2545352419__label wixui-button__label" data-testid="stylablebutton-label">Week 2</span><span class="StylableButton2545352419__icon wixui-button__icon" aria-hidden="true" data-testid="stylablebutton-icon"><div><svg data-bbox="13.05 2.55 33.878 54.8" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 60 60">
    <g>
